See http://mruckert.userweb.mwn.de/hint/web2w.html

Add the following to .bashrc:
  export SCREEN_SIZE=$(xrandr 2>/dev/null|grep connected|grep -o "[0-9]\+x[0-9]\+")
and use the companion repo http://github.com/igor-liferenko/mf-wayland
(set path to it in wayland.w)

Run as "exec /path/to/mf/plain"

To use debugger, compile with "-g -Og" flags and run "gdb plain"
